<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

<p>Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>

<p>
  We received a request to reset the password on your ProFile AI account.
  Use the code below on the password reset screen to choose a new password.
</p>

<div class="otp-box">
  <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
  <div class="otp-timer">⏱ This code expires in <%= expiryMinutes %> minutes</div>
</div>

<p class="muted">
  If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email —
  your password will remain unchanged.
</p>